ing existing\nsolutions and other variants in terms of fidelity and generality in every\nsetting. The code is available at https://scanimate.is.tue.mpg.de.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Apr 2021 17:59:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Apr 2021 06:31:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-09"}
