ary because the twin boundary\nacts as a pinning surface for the dislocation network.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Apr 2021 07:39:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 9 Apr 2021 02:38:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-12"}
